发现一个最大的问题</p>\n<ol>\n<li>偶尔的卡顿（那种超级卡，卡到没办法打字的那种），无论是 IOS 还是 mac 都会存在。</li>\n<li>跨设备复制粘贴不够灵敏，这可能是因为受限于软件级别，没办法像苹果生态系统级别复制粘贴丝滑。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>大家可以仔细想想看，为什么微信输入法启动时候打字会这么卡顿？</p>\n<ol>\n<li>同步字库？（如果异步同步处理的好，应该是不会造成卡顿）</li>\n<li>软件本身性能缺陷</li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ol>\n<p>可能大部分人会认为，我不信任并且拒绝使用这款软件，数据隐私问题，还是原生输入法好👍。</p>\n","last_modified":1711069101,"replies":60,"id":1025936},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":216769,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":4129,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":610270,"username":"oneKnow","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/oneKnow","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6100/7d90/610270_mini.png?m=1673581255","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6100/7d90/610270_normal.png?m=1673581255","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6100/7d90/610270_large.png?m=1673581255","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6100/7d90/610270_xlarge.png?m=1673581255","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6100/7d90/610270_xlarge.png?m=1673581255","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6100/7d90/610270_xlarge.png?m=1673581255","created":1673581177,"last_modified":1673581255},"last_reply_by":"Maiiiiii","last_touched":1711075937,"title":"网飞版三体上线了，有没有 v 友分享一下观后感","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1025951","created":1711071135,"deleted":0,"content":"之前宣传片出的时候站里好像挺多人讨论的，现在正片出了 v 友们觉得符合预期吗","content_rendered":"<p>之前宣传片出的时候站里好像挺多人讨论的，现在正片出了 v 友们觉得符合预期吗</p>\n","last_modified":1711071135,"replies":59,"id":1025951},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com